            "flags": {},
            "image": {},
            "name": "Short Rest",
            "ownership": {
                "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y": 3,
                "default": -1
            },
            "sort": 5,
            "src": null,
            "system": {},
            "text": {
                "content": "<p>A period of <strong>No Activity</strong> or <strong>Light Activity </strong>and is at least 1 hour long. You can only gain the benefits of 2 Short Rests per 24 hour period.</p><p><strong><em>Short Rest Benefits: </em></strong>At any point during a Short Rest, you can spend Rest Points to regain HP following the same rules as a Quick Rest. Some Features regain expended uses when you complete a Short Rest (as listed in the Feature\u2019s description).</p>",
                "format": 1
            },
            "title": {
                "level": 2,
                "show": true
            },
            "type": "text",
            "video": {
                "controls": true,
                "volume": 0.5
